&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/network-ssl/"&gt;URLError:secureConnectionFailed&lt;/a&gt; — SSL connection failures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/file-permission/"&gt;File Permission Denied&lt;/a&gt; — access permission errors.&lt;/li&gt;
